<sect2 id="gimp-layer-rotate-arbitrary">
  <title lang="en">Arbitrary Rotation</title>
  <title lang="ja">任意の回転...</title>

  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Layer</primary>
    <secondary>Transform</secondary>
    <tertiary>Rotation</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Rotate</primary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="ja">
    <primary>レイヤー</primary>
    <secondary sortas="ヘンカン">変換</secondary>
    <tertiary sortas="カイテン">回転</tertiary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="ja">
    <primary sortas="カイテン">回転</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Arbitrary Rotation</guimenuitem> command rotates a
    layer by a specified angle. It is an alternate way of accessing the
    <link linkend="gimp-tool-rotate">Rotate tool</link>. See the section
    about that tool for more information.
  </para>
  <para lang="ja">
    <guimenuitem>任意の回転...</guimenuitem> コマンドは任意の
    角度でレイヤーを回転します。 実際はこのコマンドは 
    <link linkend="gimp-tool-rotate">回転ツール</link> を呼び出します。 詳しく
    はこのツールの説明をご覧ください。
  </para>

  <sect3>
    <title lang="en">Activating the Command</title>
    <title lang="ja">コマンドの呼び出し方</title>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Layer</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>Transform</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Arbitrary Rotation</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>
        <para lang="ja">
          画像ウィンドウのメニューより
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>レイヤー</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>変換</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>任意の回転...</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="en">
          or by using the keyboard shortcut
          <keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>.
        </para>
        <para lang="ja">
          キーボードショートカット
          <keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>

  <sect3>
    <title lang="en">Example</title>
    <title lang="ja">使用例</title>
    <figure>
      <title lang="en">Applying <quote>Rotate Arbitrary</quote></title>
      <title lang="ja"><quote>任意の回転</quote>の適用</title>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/menus/layer/rotate.png" format="PNG"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>
          <para lang="en">Before applying the command</para>
          <para lang="ja">コマンド適用前</para>
        </caption>
      </mediaobject>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/menus/layer/rotate-arb.png" format="PNG"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>
          <para lang="en">
            The layer after it has been rotated 30° clockwise
          </para>
          <para lang="ja">時計回りに 30° 傾けたレイヤー</para>
        </caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </figure>
  </sect3>  
</sect2>
